data.description: Assumable 2.5% VA Loan! Captivating 4 bedroom newer home in desirable location of Arcona.  Features includes finished basement, extensive hardscaping, and outdoor kitchen with natural gas grill and firepit! ,  Electric/ Hybrid car  charging in garage! This immaculate home is "move in ready", in a quiet part of Arcona with all the amenities you would expect! Community pool and walking trails await you!  Natural gas heating, 220 service.  LVP/ Luxury Vinyl Planking in the finished basement and on the 1st floor for easy maintenance and charm.  Carpeting throughout the 2nd Floor.  Total Finished  Sq. Footage over 3000 SF! Arcona is a  very warm, welcoming, and diverse community with a mixture of working professionals, families, and retirees on every block. This  house in particular is in a quieter part of the neighborhood, but only a few blocks, or short walk down the walking path to the town center area where there are boutiques, Thea, Springate Vineyard, Idea Coffee, a HOA member gym, Shirley Rae's Ice Cream, and Amore Pizza. The location is very convenient to all major highways 15, 83, 581, 81, and 76 and a short drive away from Harrisburg International Airport. There are a lot of great places to shop within 5-20 minutes as well.
